<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 12:27:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普模因币在海湖庄园活动上大放异彩，营销总统</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/trump-memecoin-jumps-on-mar-a-lago-event-marketing-the-president</link><description>带有唐纳德·特朗普名字的模因币在过去 24 小时内飙升了 60%，此前其发起人在海湖庄园宣传了一场以总统为主角的独家晚会——尽管白宫尚未证实他是否出席。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwYGTmF8jOWE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 20:14:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/trump-memecoin-jumps-on-mar-a-lago-event-marketing-the-president</guid></item><item><title>比特币触及近期交易区间顶部后涨幅回落</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-edges-higher-in-asia-despite-middle-east-jitters</link><description>随着中东动荡继续冲击全球市场，比特币攀升至近期交易区间的上限，之后最大的加密货币回吐涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivgEuwjOyR4A/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 02:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-edges-higher-in-asia-despite-middle-east-jitters</guid></item><item><title>比特币接近过去熊市触底的区域</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-nears-zone-where-past-bear-markets-have-bottomed-out</link><description>一位曾投资过之前三个繁荣和萧条周期的加密货币基金经理表示，自 10 月份以来，比特币的价值已下跌近一半，历史上标志着过去低迷结束的一系列指标表明，抛售可能正在进入最后阶段。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i7haQl9CopKU/v1/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 14:29:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-nears-zone-where-past-bear-markets-have-bottomed-out</guid></item></channel></rss>